This is the best sauce ever - even my kids love it. The one problem I had the first time I made it was that the sauce was much too sweet. I was able to successfully adjust the sweetness with lemon juice (and it tasted amazing). In subsequent years I have made the sauce with only 2/3 cup of brown sugar to begin with. I then add brown sugar or lemon juice to get the taste I want. I suspect that I've been using cheaper and sweeter Marsala wine than others out there, but I don't mind saving the money, and it tastes incredible in the end!

